OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Stacey Poole
OL,7,Freports on weight loss jabs trial.
OL,9,FScientists at the University of
OL,10,FSouthampton have launched a pioneering
OL,11,Ftrial into whether weight loss jabs
OL,12,Fcan help treat breast cancer.
OL,14,FThere's been a significant rise in the
OL,15,Fnumber of women being diagnosed with
OL,16,Fthe disease, who are under 50 and it's
OL,17,Ffelt obesity and lifestyle could be a
OL,18,Ffactor.
OL,20,FSo why does obesity make women so much
OL,21,Fmore vulnerable?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
