OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773321081
OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FProfessor Simon Lord from Oxford
OL,7,FUniversity believes it's three main
OL,8,Freasons.
OL,10,FIt often causes higher oestrogen
OL,11,Flevels and higher levels of diabetes
OL,12,Fand insulin, all linked to higher
OL,13,Flevels of cancer.
OL,15,FObesity also causes inflammation
OL,16,Fthroughout the body which can damage
OL,17,Fhealthy cells.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
