CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773321081
OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FThe Against Breast Cancer Charity has
OL,7,Freceived a donation of #243,000, to
OL,8,Fsee if drugs like Ozempic and other
OL,9,FGLP-1 agonists can not only reduce
OL,10,Fpatients weight, but also enhance the
OL,11,Feffectiveness of treatments like
OL,12,Fimmunotherapy in obese cancer patients.
OL,14,FThe study will try and understand why
OL,15,Fcancer spreads more in obese patients
OL,16,Fand why some treatments like
OL,17,Fimmunotherapy are less effective.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
