FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773321081
OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FThe team at Southampton's centre for
OL,7,FCancer Immunology will not use real
OL,8,Fpatients, but instead 3D laboratory
OL,9,Fmodels in the hope of providing enough
OL,10,Fdata for clinical patient led trials
OL,11,Fto begin.
OL,13,FIt follows trials on other diabetes
OL,14,Fmedication like Metformin which showed
OL,15,Fthey can reactivate immune cells and
OL,16,Fmake antibody therapies work more
OL,17,Feffectively.
OL,19,FResearchers are hoping the weight loss
OL,20,Fdrugs have a similar effect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
