OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773321081
OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FBecause this medication already exists
OL,7,Fand has been shown to be well
OL,8,Ftolerated in patients, if scientists
OL,9,Fdo show these jabs can improve
OL,10,Ftreatment outcomes they could be added
OL,11,Finto treatment programmes very quickly.
OL,13,FThis is an exciting development in the
OL,14,Ftreatment of Breast Cancer and medics
OL,15,Fwant to reassure women that although
OL,16,Fcancer rates are rising, treatment
OL,17,Foptions are improving all the time and
OL,18,Foutcomes for women have never been
OL,19,Fbetter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
