OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773321081
OL,3,CCould weight loss jabs help treat
OL,4,Cbreast cancer?
OL,6,FBut in order to reduce your chances
OL,7,Fdoctors have stressed that women
OL,8,Fshould keep their weight within
OL,9,Fhealthy limits, keep alcohol
OL,10,Fconsumption to a minimum and stop
OL,11,Fsmoking.
OL,13,FThey add regular exercise and eating a
OL,14,Fbalanced diet is also very important.
OL,16,FBut screening is also crucial.
OL,18,FThe results of the trial are expected
OL,19,Fin three years' time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
